Cîroc Kenya partnered with Blue Door during the celebrations of New Year, offering consumers an outstanding performance from Sol Generation, a renown record label company owned by Sauti Sol. On one of Nairobi's largest celebration for the end-of-year festivities, attendees got to experience a one-of-a-kind performance coupled with world-class cocktails and great conversation. Among those who performed were Bensoul, Kaskazini and Art In Motion dancers.